Using the ebuilds:
	USE=git emerge layman
	layman -a maza https://github.com/mazacoin/portage-overlay.git

Whenever you update (emerge --sync), also run:
	layman -S

Come to freenode #maza-dev  nd let us know if you'd like to help out :) 

This is adapted from overlay from bitcoin-gentoo https://gitlab.com/bitcoin/gentoo.git
More bitcoin related packages can be found in that overlay

